><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184200/extras/ca88f97e114775c357687990207f8de7.poster.avif?t=1726840166\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184200/extras/ca88f97e114775c357687990207f8de7.webm?t=1726840166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184200/extras/ca88f97e114775c357687990207f8de7.mp4?t=1726840166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184200/extras/a1f2e7cd8d0d65043662735999590bab.poster.avif?t=1726840166\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184200/extras/a1f2e7cd8d0d65043662735999590bab.webm?t=1726840166\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3184200/extras/a1f2e7cd8d0d65043662735999590bab.mp4?t=1726840166\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the Lightless World it is your choice either to play solo or cooperate with a friend to fight the Order of the Dawn.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><br><strong>Reverse Horror</strong>: In this game you take the role of the &quot;bad&quot; guys, playing as one of the archdemons.<br><br><strong>Diverse Character Progression</strong>: As you delve deeper into the game, you'll collect powerful items, discover new abilities, and encounter a variety of unique characters. Customize your hero's build and playstyle, adapting to the challenges of each run.<br><br><strong>Challenging Enemies and Bosses</strong>: Face off against a wide array of menacing foes, from swarms of lesser humans to formidable angelic bosses. Strategic combat and effective use of your character's abilities are essential for success.  <br><br><strong>Random Events and Challenges</strong>: Throughout the map, players encounter random events, challenges, and hidden secrets. These can range from temporal anomalies altering gameplay mechanics to mysterious portals offering valuable rewards or increased difficulty.<br><br><strong>Artistic Visuals and Dynamic Soundtrack</strong>: Immerse yourself in a visually stunning, ever-shifting environment filled with atmospheric lighting and intricate details. The dynamic soundtrack adapts to the intensity of the gameplay, heightening the sense of tension and excitement.  <br><br><strong>Character Progression</strong>: As players delve deeper into the game, they collect resources, discover powerful artifacts and unlock new abilities!<br><br><strong>Skill Tree</strong>: In The Lightless World, players embark on a journey of power by navigating a intricate talent tree. This branching system, offers players the opportunity to customize and specialize their character's abilities, shaping their unique playstyle. <br><br>As players gain experience points and level up, they earn skill points that can be invested in the talent tree. Unlocking a specific talent often requires points to be allocated in prerequisite skills in that path, promoting a sense of progression and specialization. The choices players make in the talent tree directly influences their character strengths, weaknesses and playstyle.",
